      <T n="text">0xB25395F1<!--String: "Do you have a weird suspicion that someone you know has <b><font color='#199C2C'>buried some deep family secret</font></b>? Perhaps they Forged a false Family Connection, or perhaps they have a Secret Child?\n\nThe best way to investigate is through a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Family Tree Compendium</font></b>! Go to <b><font color='#199C2C'>Build Mode</font></b> to acquire one, then return to Live mode and interact with it to choose whether to research your own family or someone else's.\n\nIf there's something <b><font color='#199C2C'>Scandalous</font></b> to be found, there's a decent chance your Sim might discover it! If not, you can try researching again at a later time."--></T>
